ive.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-19T13:24:37.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"springload/awesome-wagtail","categoryHTML":"<h2>Apps</h2><h3>Misc</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/torchbox/wagtail-content-import\">Wagtail Content Import</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/torchbox/wagtail-content-import\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">24</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":24,\"repo\":\"torchbox/wagtail-content-import\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Import content from Google Docs or Docx into StreamFields, using a customisable mapping system.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-19T13:24:37.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"springload/awesome-wagtail","categoryHTML":"<h2>Apps</h2><h3>Widgets</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wagtail/wagtail-generic-chooser\">wagtail-generic-chooser</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/wagtail/wagtail-generic-chooser\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">95</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":95,\"repo\":\"wagtail/wagtail-generic-chooser\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - provides base classes for building chooser popups and form widgets for the Wagtail admin, matching the look and feel of Wagtail's built-in choosers for pages, documents, snippets and images.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-19T13:23:05.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"edm00se/awesome-board-games","categoryHTML":"<h2>Family</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/245271/forbidden-sky\">Forbidden Sky</a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Soar to dizzying heights in the electrifying cooperative adventure. Work as a team to explore a mysterious platform that floats at the center of a savage storm. Connect a circuit of cables to launch a secret rocket — all before you are struck by lightning or blown off to the depths below. It's a high-wire act that will test your team's capacity for courage and cooperation. One false step and you all could be grounded.This latest installment in the Forbidden that game series takes you to new heights with several novel challenges, including collectively planning a terrain using only limited information and constructing a real electrical circuit.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/itemrep/img/zu-kq_Fnq8twvfhPG5PevtT4z5E=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic4177924.jpg\" alt=\"Forbidden Sky image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2 - 5</td>\n<td align=\"right\">10</td>\n<td align=\"right\">60m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2020-10-19T12:44:35.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"edm00se/awesome-board-games","categoryHTML":"<h2>Family</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/194655/santorini\">Santorini</a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Santorini is an accessible strategy game, simple enough for an elementary school classroom while aiming to provide gameplay depth and content for hardcore gamers to explore, The rules are simple. Each turn consists of 2 steps. those are Move (move one of your builders into a neighboring space) and Build (construct a building level adjacent to the builder you move). If either of your builders reaches the third level, you win.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/itemrep/img/8vG-UtGeFbhMXPTzLDUOqWot8hA=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic3283110.png\" alt=\"Santorini Image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2 - 4</td>\n<td align=\"right\">8</td>\n<td align=\"right\">20m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2020-10-19T12:39:21.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"awesome-foss/awesome-sysadmin","categoryHTML":"<h2>Client management</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://just-install.github.io/\">just-install</a> – Python script for downloading and silently installing MSI files.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-19T12:31:03.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"edm00se/awesome-board-games","categoryHTML":"<h2>Family</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/123540/tokaido\">Tokaido</a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>In Tokaido, each player is a traveler crossing the \"East sea road\", one of the most magnificent roads of Japan. While traveling, you will meet people, taste fine meals, collect beautiful items, discover great panoramas, and visit temples and wild places but at the end of the day, when everyone has arrived at the end of the road you'll have to be the most initiated traveler – which means that you'll have to be the one who discovered the most interesting and varied things. All of the actions in Tokaido are very simple, and combined with a unique graphic design, Tokaido offers players a peaceful zen mood in its play.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/itemrep/img/oNPKz7nD6d53yT7CDIquGw6moNg=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic3747956.png\" alt=\"Tokaido Image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2 - 5</td>\n<td align=\"right\">8</td>\n<td align=\"right\">45m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2020-10-19T12:28:11.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"johnjago/awesome-free-software","categoryHTML":"<h2>Software</h2><h3>Web Applications</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.getdnote.com/\">Dnote</a> - A simple command line notebook with multi-device sync and web interface. (<a href=\"https://github.com/dnote/dnote/blob/master/licenses/AGPLv3.txt\">GNU AGPLv3</a>)</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-19T10:22:48.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"scholtzm/awesome-steam","categoryHTML":"<h2>Packages</h2><h4>Trading</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/itsjfx/node-steam-inventory-api-ng\">steam-inventory-api-ng</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/itsjfx/node-steam-inventory-api-ng\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2,\"repo\":\"itsjfx/node-steam-inventory-api-ng\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A Steam Inventory API wrapper with advanced features such as retries and proxy support.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-19T09:26:23.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"scholtzm/awesome-steam","categoryHTML":"<h2>Packages</h2><h4>Misc</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://gi